children.name: Search the buy car with model
Search the buy car with model
Given I am on homepage
When I mouse hover on "buy + sell" tab
And I click Search Cars link
Then I navigate to new and used car search page
And I select make "Audi"
And I select model "A1"
And I select location "NT - South"
And I select price "$40,000"
And I click on Find My Next Car tab
Then I should see the make "Audi" in results
